nts, Resignations, Deaths (4/14/2017)\"</a>. <i>The Chronicle of Higher Education</i>. The Chronicle of Higher Education<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2018-09-16</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Chronicle+of+Higher+Education&amp;rft.atitle=Appointments%2C+Resignations%2C+Deaths+%284%2F14%2F2017%29&amp;rft.date=2017-04-14&amp;rft.aulast=Strickland&amp;rft.aufirst=Anais&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chronicle.com%2Farticle%2FAppointments-Resignations%2F239728&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMona+Shattell\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-butje2008-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-butje2008_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Butje, Andrea; Repede, Elizabeth; Shattell, Mona M. (1 October 2008). \"Healing Scents\". <i>Journal of Psychosocial Nursing and Mental Health Services</i>. <b>46</b> (10): 46\u201352. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.3928/02793695-20081001-12\">10.3928/02793695-20081001-12</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Psychosocial+Nursing+and+Mental+Health+Services&amp;rft.atitle=Healing+Scents&amp;rft.volume=46&amp;rft.issue=10&amp;rft.pages=46-52&amp;rft.date=2008-10-01&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.3928%2F02793695-20081001-12&amp;rft.aulast=Butje&amp;rft.aufirst=Andrea&amp;rft.au=Repede%2C+Elizabeth&amp;rft.au=Shattell%2C+Mona+M.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMona+Shattell\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-pmid17635627-8\"><span class=\"mw